---
title:
  nl: "E-Learning ontwikkelen"
  de: "E-Learning"
  en: "E-Learning"
description:
  nl: E-learning wordt een succes met Defacto als ervaren en technisch onderlegde partner
  de: Die Qualität im Krankenhaus lässt sich durch E-Learning für alle Mitarbeiter nachhaltig verbessern. Defacto hilft Ihnen bei Installation und Umsetzung.
  en: E-learning within your organisation will become a success with Defacto as an experienced and technically skilled partner
popup: false
---

<section class="gray">
  <div class="row">
    <h1><%= t("elearning.heading") %></h1>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="row">
    <article class="sidebar-content">
      <%= partial "elearning/elearning" %>
    </article>
    <%= partial "diensten/sidebar" %>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="gray" id="ebook-download">
  <div class="row">

    <label for="ebook-email">
      <h3><%= t("elearning_ebook.heading_html") %></h3>
      <%= image_tag "book-#{I18n.locale.to_s}.png", alt: t("elearning_ebook.image_alt") %>
    </label>

    <form class="form-inline" accept-charset="UTF-8" action="<%= t("urls.ebook") %>" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="utf8" value="✓">
      <input type="hidden" name="form" value="<%= t("elearning_ebook.formkeep_title") %>">
      <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="<%= t("form.name") %>">
      <input type="text" name="organisation" placeholder="<%= t("form.organisation") %>" required>
      <input type="email" name="email" id="ebook-email" placeholder="<%= t("form.email") %>" required>
      <input type="hidden" name="download" value="<%= full_url(data.downloads.ebook[I18n.locale]) %>">
      <button type="submit"><%= t("actions.download") %></button>
    </form>

  </div>
</section>

<%= partial "clients/clients-section" %>
